post_text: #TeamSISD was the FIRST district in the region to open an early college high school in 2006. The district opened THREE MORE early college programs within a three-year span. #TeamSISD will be the ONLY district in the region to offer an early college program at EVERY high school!
text: #TeamSISD was the FIRST district in the region to open an early college high school in 2006. The district opened THREE MORE early college programs within a three-year span. #TeamSISD will be the ONLY district in the region to offer an early college program at EVERY high school!

post_text: The three new early college programs will give more #TeamSISD high school students the opportunity to get ahead and save money in future college costs. The early colleges allow students to complete their high school requirements while taking college-level courses.

post_text: Cactus Trails Elementary is the first Bond 2017 project to be completed. It was built on time and within budget. The school follows a proto-typical design, similar to Carrasco and Purple Heart Elementary, with an open space concept and flexible, collaborative design spaces.
